OL,3,CFormer Deputy Chief Constable under
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation
OL,6,FThe former Deputy Chief Constable of
OL,7,FGloucestershire Police is under
OL,8,Fcriminal investigation, it has been
OL,9,Frevealed.
OL,11,FAccording to Gloucestershire Police,
OL,12,FShaun West is being investigated in
OL,13,Frelation to a number of serious
OL,14,Fallegations including assault and
OL,15,Fmisconduct in public office.
OL,17,FMr West is also being investigated by
OL,18,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,19,FConduct (IOPC). He retired in June
OL,20,F2024 after he was suspended by Chief
OL,21,FConstable Rod Hansen in January.
