OL,3,CFormer Deputy Chief Constable under
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation
OL,6,FThese latest allegations came to light
OL,7,Fafter the current Chief Constable was
OL,8,Fsuspended for alleged gross misconduct.
OL,10,FGloucestershire Police issued a
OL,11,Fstatement, which reads: "We understand
OL,12,Fthat both the communities we serve,
OL,13,Fand our own workforce, will be
OL,14,Fconcerned and unsettled following the
OL,15,Fsuspension of Chief Constable Rod
OL,16,FHansen.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
