OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1728638744
OL,3,CFormer Deputy Chief Constable under
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation
OL,6,F"We are continuing to provide the best
OL,7,Fservice we can to our communities, and
OL,8,Fwe would like to assure everyone that
OL,9,Ffrontline policing will not stop, and
OL,10,Fwe will continue to respond to calls
OL,11,Ffrom those who need us.
OL,13,F"We have dedicated and hardworking
OL,14,Fofficers, police staff and volunteers
OL,15,Fwho will continue to keep people safe
OL,16,Ffrom harm, pursue offenders and
OL,17,Finvestigate crime.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
