OL,3,CFormer Deputy Chief Constable under
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation
OL,6,F"Chief Constable Rod Hansen was
OL,7,Fsuspended by Police and Crime
OL,8,FCommissioner (PCC) Chris Nelson on
OL,9,FMonday (7 October), following the
OL,10,Flaunch of an investigation by the
OL,11,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,12,F(IOPC).
OL,14,F"The IOPC confirmed it is
OL,15,Finvestigating conduct allegations
OL,16,Fagainst Chief Constable Hansen
OL,17,Frelating to his handling of an
OL,18,Fallegation against a member of staff,
OL,19,Fand whether relevant policies and
OL,20,Fprocedures were subsequently followed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
