OL,3,CFormer Deputy Chief Constable under
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation
OL,6,F"Former Deputy Chief Constable Shaun
OL,7,FWest retired in June 2024, and he also
OL,8,Fremains subject to an IOPC
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,F"He is under criminal investigation in
OL,12,Frelation to a number of serious
OL,13,Fallegations including assault and
OL,14,Fmisconduct in public office. He was
OL,15,Fsuspended by Chief Constable Hansen in
OL,16,FJanuary 2024 after the IOPC launched
OL,17,Fan investigation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
