OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1728638744
OL,3,CFormer Deputy Chief Constable under
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation
OL,6,F"The Office of the Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner (OPCC) is working with
OL,8,FHis Majesty's Inspectorate of
OL,9,FConstabulary and Fire & Rescue
OL,10,FServices (HMICFRS) and the College of
OL,11,FPolicing to identify a temporary Chief
OL,12,FConstable who can lead the
OL,13,FConstabulary and provide consistency
OL,14,Fduring this period.
OL,16,F"We are unable to comment further on
OL,17,Fthe investigations as that is a matter
OL,18,Ffor the IOPC.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
