OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1728638744
OL,3,CFormer Deputy Chief Constable under
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation
OL,6,F"We want to reassure people the
OL,7,Fremaining members of the Chief Officer
OL,8,FGroup (COG) and the wider Executive
OL,9,FBoard will provide continuity of
OL,10,Fleadership until a temporary Chief
OL,11,FConstable is in place, and senior
OL,12,Fleaders across the organisation met
OL,13,Fyesterday (Tuesday 8 October) to
OL,14,Fensure our important work continues as
OL,15,Fnormal.
OL,17,F"In Gloucestershire, we have three
OL,18,FAssistant Chief Constables (ACCs), one
OL,19,Fof whom is temporary, and an Assistant
OL,20,FChief Officer (ACO), all of whom are
OL,21,Fhighly experienced officers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
