OL,3,CFormer Deputy Chief Constable under
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation
OL,6,F"While the situation is unusual, it
OL,7,Fisn't unprecedented, and we'd like to
OL,8,Freassure our communities, staff and
OL,9,Fpartner organisations we continue to
OL,10,Foperate as normal.
OL,12,F"As soon as there is any developments
OL,13,For changes to our leadership group we
OL,14,Fwill provide a further update."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
